<h6 id="graphql-query-1">graphql query</h6>
<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>mutation myMutation($user:CreateUserInput!){
  createUser(input:$user){
    id
    name
  }
}

Query variables
{
  "user": {
    "title": "Hello, world!!!!"
  }
}
</code></pre></div></div>

